        "subject": "LU-9120 lnet: LNet Health/Resiliency Feature",
        "message": "LU-9120 lnet: LNet Health/Resiliency Feature\n\nThe LNet Health/Resiliency feature adds the ability for LNet to try\nout different interfaces available to it if message sending fails.\nIt maintains the health of each remote and local interfaces and\nselects the best interface for sending from and best remote\ninterface to send to.\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <ashehata@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Iec024a660460fc78478fcedad679f1234b927465\n"
